steps.body:
Each path through the tree is an application of the multiplication rule $P(A \cap B) = P(A) \times P(B \mid A)$:

$$
P(R_1 \cap R_2) = \frac{5}{8} \times \frac{4}{7} = \frac{20}{56} = \frac{5}{14}
$$

$$
P(R_1 \cap B_2) = \frac{5}{8} \times \frac{3}{7} = \frac{15}{56}
$$

$$
P(B_1 \cap R_2) = \frac{3}{8} \times \frac{5}{7} = \frac{15}{56}
$$

$$
P(B_1 \cap B_2) = \frac{3}{8} \times \frac{2}{7} = \frac{6}{56} = \frac{3}{28}
$$
